16:
I know you tagged along because
you wanted the extra training, but
I'm not sure you need it.
19:
Hey, newbie? What was that move
you pulled just now? You gotta
teach me that one!
22:
We'll be set for a while with a haul
like this! This calls for a celebration!
30:
We're feasting tonight, and we're not
starting without the man of the hour!
38: Haha, did you see his face just now?
41:
Looked like a lost little duckling. He'll
get used to the chaos soon enough.
50: I can't hear ya, lad! Speak up!
59:
Look at that, Mr. Popular came to sit
with us.
64:
M-my head's been spinning this
whole time. There's just so much to
take in...
67: We really are in another world, huh?
72:
Haha... Amazing, isn't it? You should
enjoy yourself while you're here.
74:
There's also plenty for you to learn
along the way.
81:
I do. This place is filled with all sorts
of interesting things, though it's up
to you to seek them out.
84:
Lad, what're you doing in the corner?
Come drink over here!
88: U-um... I can walk by myself!
91: ...That last one was pretty tough, eh?
92:
Yeah, I ain't never saw one that big
before, even when I was a knight.
Can't believe you took it down, just
like that.
95:
You were a knight before? Then why
did you become an adventurer?
97:
Lots of reasons. A lot of the people
here didn't choose this lifethis life
chose them.
98:
Sure. You know, apparently the old
man in our group used to be some
sorta legendary thief.
99:
Ah, those rumors are true. We nearly
killed each other several times back
when I was a knight.
105:
If you two used to be enemies... How
can you fight as allies now?
108:
Don't get the wrong idea, lad. Me
and him ain't allies or pals or
anything.
109:
We're coworkers, and we'll keep
working together...
111:
As long as we have the loot from the
Kaleidoscope! Payday's what
matters when all's said and done!
122:
For better or for worse, they only see
the treasure in front of them.
129:
They're a rough bunch, but they get
along... Just taking one day at a
time together...
133:
What if we had a place like this in
our world?
139: You want a Palpebra for our world?
142:
Yeah, that city is amazing! All sorts
of people work together toward the
same goal!
145:
I think it kind of resembles the ideal
world that we're trying to make.
149:
Hmm. I get what you're trying to
say...
151:
But Palpebra's got that
Kaleidoscopea never-ending
treasure trove.
154:
People can work together because
there's a decent reward, you know?
158:
I'm sorry... I got so excited, I didn't
think it through...
161:
Oh, don't get so down. I actually
think you're onto something.
164:
We've got that burny gloop stuff,
remember? I'm thinking we can turn
that stuff into our own Kaleidoscope.
168:
Our ideas are on the same track. So
don't hold back whenever you've got
something to say.
171: After all, we're in this together!
177: I'll help out however I can!
